title: Ep. - 435 - THE BEATLES: GET BACK SISTER WIVES AND REAL HOUSEWIVES OF SALT LAKE CITY
description:
Kate discusses this week’s episodes of Real Housewives of Salt Lake City and Sister Wives.

 

Veteran unscripted TV producer Eliot Goldberg discusses The Beatles: Get Back, a documentary series covering the making of the Beatles' 1970 album Let It Be (which had the working title of Get Back) and draws largely from unused footage and audio material originally captured for the identically titled 1970 documentary of the album by Michael Lindsay-Hogg.
